                <p>You warrant that you are 18 years of age or over and have legal capacity to use the Site and to create a legally binding contract with the relevant accommodation provider. You warrant that all Personal Information submitted during accommodation booking is correct and you accept financial responsibility for all transactions made under your name or account. You undertake that the credit or debit card you use to secure your booking is your own and that there are sufficient funds to cover the cost of the booking you make with us.  In the event that you suspect credit or debit card fraud or unauthorised use of your card by third parties, you should contact your bank or card issuer immediately. </p>
