                <h3 id="c4">
                    Reviews and Content Guidelines
                </h3>
                <p>
                    You agree to post Contributions in accordance with the following Guidelines. We will not publish a Contribution unless it follows these Guidelines. These Guidelines are not exhaustive and LateRooms reserves the right to vary them from time to time and the Guidelines published at the time of browsing shall be those in effect.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Format requirements - We will only accept images in a .jpg, .jpeg, .gif or .png format. We will not accept images smaller than 430 x 322 or files larger than 5MB
                    </li>
                    <li>No unlawful or objectionable content - this means your Contribution should not contain images, words, actions or content that is or may be considered unlawful, defamatory, libellous, abusive, racially or sexually offensive or obscene
                    </li>
                    <li>Original - content of Contributions should not infringe the intellectual property rights or other proprietary rights of others that shall include copyright, trademark, privacy or trade secrets
                    </li>
                    <li>Harmful content - Contribution shall not contain viruses, worms, Trojan horses or other computer program that may damage or affect any system or data
                    </li>
                    <li>No spamming or advertising - Contribution shall not contain commercial web or e-mail addresses and no promotional or advertising material of any kind including the pricing and availability information and alternative ordering information
                    </li>
                    <li>No HTML tags
                    </li>
                    <li>Contributors should not use false e-mail addresses, impersonate others or in any way mislead as to their identity. LateRooms confirms that any personal identifiable information such as addresses, phone numbers or URL's will be removed and reviews or contributions may not be published
                    </li>
                    <li>Contributors under the age of 18 should get the permission of a parent or guardian before submitting any review or contribution.
                    </li>
                </ul>
